# Snapshot of the DCAT distribution metadata for the "WC-Standorte" dataset's GeoJSON
# distribution of the Landeshauptstadt München (open.bydata dataset
# 80832bca-499b-4b24-bb41-9e77f0ef31ee, GeoJSON distribution
# 1f90f05d-5d8c-4222-9353-c9e30b63d3e3), captured locally.
# build-graph.js fetches the toilet points live from the WFS but reads dct:modified
# from here to stamp it onto the toilets — analogous to the playgrounds and fountains.
<https://open.bydata.de/api/hub/repo/distributions/1f90f05d-5d8c-4222-9353-c9e30b63d3e3>
    a dcat:Distribution ;
    dct:modified "2026-06-08T06:47:09Z"^^xsd:dateTime .
